name: The Empty Shelves Dungeon Delve
description:
The monsters in the dungeon haven't returned their library books! It's up to Library Goblin to hunt the missing books down, and maybe help a friend along the way.

Move with WASD or the arrow keys. Try talking to characters more than once.

Made with Bitsy and Bitsy Savior for the Overdue Library Books Jam. The cover font is Morris Roman by Dieter Steffmann.
